   139	
   140	4. **Wire-binding scenarios** (chapter 07):
   141	   - Status-code mapping per §§2-6: every operation returns the
   142	     spec-pinned status.
   143	   - RFC 7807 problem+json envelope shape on every non-2xx response per
   144	     §7 (content-type, all five envelope fields, `type` matching
   145	     `eden://error/<name>`).
   146	   - Closed `eden://error/<name>` vocabulary per §7: every error type
   147	     observed across the suite belongs to the closed table; every
   148	     entry in the table is observed at least once across the suite.
   149	   - `X-Eden-Experiment-Id` header **disagreement** is rejected with
